A note on large lab pink pear proportions: pear diamonds above 4ct tend toward elongated L/W ratios (1.55–1.75+) that produce a longer, narrower teardrop. Verify the specific L/W ratio via HD 360° video before purchasing. Full pear proportion guidance in the **[pear cut diamond buying guide](/pear-cut-diamond)**.

