The [GIA 1.01ct Fancy Brownish Pink SI1](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-29465842?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) at [$12,403](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/pink-29465842?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is the highest-clarity Brownish Pink 1ct pear in this tier — SI1 over SI2 for a $1,246 premium. For a pink diamond where color is primary, SI1 vs. SI2 is a marginal optical upgrade that may not justify the cost; prioritize reviewing both via 360° video.

